Join us for ACS's 150th Anniversary Celebration

2026

In 2026, we're celebrating 150 years of breakthroughs, connections, and real-world solutions that make life better. Chemistry shapes everything around us, and we're taking that message across the country and around the world.

Be part of the movement!
